a95c2e347d8541455e53a76975a256349c1c6d9","tid":332641,"uid":43239,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T14:10:26.000Z","msg":"真正揸得起車根本唔會在乎炒車<br />\n阻住我行就撞落去<br />\n理撚得撞死人入去坐幾年<br />\n成日守交通規則嘅人唔該反省下"},{"pid":"65c2e2a42e692061346931663bfe20b7bade5bad","tid":332641,"uid":28418,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T17:53:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 咁唔泊停車場？<br />\n逼係條街做乜撚"},{"pid":"9f360c5b597943f1ca06b7d16da28ec1b1755688","tid":332641,"uid":47023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T23:15:48.000Z","msg":"抄牌事小，驚返黎架車俾人拖走唔知點返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6889d8d509f3e81c348002b712fbc3cb4c3dcb7","tid":332641,"uid":18241,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T23:31:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抄牌事小，驚返黎架車俾人拖走唔知點返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真正揸得起車根本唔會在乎架車比人拖走<br />\n<br />\n周街都係錢七, 即時比十皮野個司機實肯即刻賣比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04eeea37496579fdbd6051a4f2488b054c9efdde","tid":332641,"uid":200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T23:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母 阻撚住晒</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b44fd78b929163461f1cb05ab6f8e178aa93f8","tid":332641,"uid":50101,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:16:41.000Z","msg":"以前車場十蚊粒鐘，抄一張覺得好金，而家四十蚊粒鐘，停得三四個鐘就覺得三百二搏得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c3949e8c1c4af1cf3c880a690cfe29cd4eebfd","tid":332641,"uid":123827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:17:41.000Z","msg":"唔關金額事<br />\n係無喇喇跌錢果下唔抵姐<br />\n每架車缸油都唔只320<br />\n但問題係320用黎自用定用黎俾政府咁解"},{"pid":"e25feafde7ccff0cc8f962ec2c01353116ba4e69","tid":332641,"uid":123827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T