a","tid":332641,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:27:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"086a5bb81355bde790e3cea2430d1bf67fa0d684","tid":332641,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都唔一定<br />\n識人有過億身家但係勁吝嗇</blockquote><br />\n正解 係窮撚先會成日幻想有錢人好疏爽<br />\n其實好多有錢人一分一毫都唔會亂洗</blockquote><br />\n睇性格啦<br />\n<br />\n可能唔亂洗錢先做到有錢人<br />\n<br />\n不過富二代如果家教差就亂洗錢，老蘭見唔少"},{"pid":"a5aca89fa40b832fcf3726a366f9277db2067ea4","tid":332641,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都唔一定<br />\n識人有過億身家但係勁吝嗇</blockquote><br />\n我同你諗既係咪同一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都諗到一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2091be1855745ce3f5dcf6a0cb7cc1986036df55","tid":332641,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:21:21.000Z","msg":"真係有錢就請司機啦，仲撚洗自己揸？"}]}